{"tid":1019838,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"雪橇犬疑看見主人太興奮　3樓躍下砸傷湖南67歲翁頸椎脊髓","createTime":"2019-02-13T08:03:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-13T10:36:30.000Z","uid":130626,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"9fd05b2390c78d25e0c4f561cae3eb5c30c4473d","tid":1019838,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T08:03:26.000Z","msg":"湖南一戶劉姓人家年初五（9日）向親友拜年後返家，沒想到才走到樓下，突然有東西從天而降，砸中67歲男主人，劉男當場暈倒，醒來後才知道，砸中他的竟然是自己養的雪橇犬&hellip;&hellip;。<br />\n據早前報道，這隻體重約30公斤的雪橇犬，幾個月前才被位於湖南新田縣的劉家收養，當天因為看到主人回來實在太興奮了，竟然從3樓一躍而下飛撲主人。劉男說，「當時他還以為面前有牆塌了。」<br />\n劉男暈倒後，立即被送醫至郴州市第一人民醫院，由於頸椎骨折脫位、脊髓損傷，將進行手術治療。醫師也對雪橇犬肇事感到相當訝異，「我還從來沒有見過因為被狗狗砸倒造成這樣的傷情。」事後主人並未怪罪愛犬，而只是用鐵鏈將其鎖好，防止同類事件再次發生。<br />\n網民得知罕見的狗砸暈人意外後，紛紛笑說「雪橇犬又幹大事！」，紛紛調侃養雪橇犬會有生命危險&hellip;&hellip;。但也有人說幸好受傷的是自己主人，要是弄傷他人麻煩可就大囉。<br />\n（三湘都市報）<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2430653/org/b242e27ce65669d9e500e8ba95c310d6.jpg/DmyhsyNMSlOmjKZjKo4TE1ZxazSTyOkW9H70tfR-9LU?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2430653%2Forg%2Fb242e27ce65669d9e500e8ba95c310d6.jpg%2FDmyhsyNMSlOmjKZjKo4TE1ZxazSTyOkW9H70tfR-9LU%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=b456c77a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2430657/org/4ec6118b032f2f1f2c8227071a9c6b17.jpg/gV1dR6hzzzKzl8vr24KkV1Ahrd4Qg10-61jDV-tYw1c\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2430657%2Forg%2F4ec6118b032f2f1f2c8227071a9c6b17.jpg%2FgV1dR6hzzzKzl8vr24KkV1Ahrd4Qg10-61jDV-tYw1c&h=c4b26180&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2430658/org/883b7569b471cd0fe89aaf4782006030.jpg/YNUdEamLLqoGrhndHSQOnLbHZJSu9EYvovnl1qL55dY\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2430658%2Forg%2F883b7569b471cd0fe89aaf4782006030.jpg%2FYNUdEamLLqoGrhndHSQOnLbHZJSu9EYvovnl1qL55dY&h=9f7c9577&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/IQ6yJy